column3: CREATE DATABASE `inventory` CHARSET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci

CREATE TABLE `sales` (
  `usergender` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `usercity` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `usersentiment` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zipcode` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `sku` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `createdate` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `category` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `price` decimal(12,5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `county` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `countycode` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `userstate` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  `categorygroup` mediumtext DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`createdate`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

CREATE TABLE `debezium_signals` (
  `id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `data` varchar(2048) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci
